《失落的星球：极限状态》得到了媒体较为正面至褒贬不一的评价，《失落的星球》Xbox 360版在评论聚合网站[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]和[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]分别得到了78.56%的<ref name=GRX360 />和79分的汇总评分（满分为100分）<ref name="MCX360" />，而PlayStation 3版则为70.19%<ref name=GRPS3 />和67分的汇总评分<ref name="MCPS3" />，PC版为67%<ref name=GRPC />和66分的汇总评分<ref name="MCPC" />。日本的游戏杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》更是给予本作36/40的高度评价。游戏网站[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]称《失落的星球》“令人印象深刻”<ref name="gsutracrec">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12326|title=Critical Reception: Capcom's Lost Planet: Extreme Condition|last=Cowan|first=Danny|date=01-10-2007|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728182928/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12326|archivedate=2009-07-28}}</ref>，其视觉效果和战斗场景也备受好评<ref name="ign360review3" /><ref name="gspotpcreview" />。但也有评论家批评其操控手感、配音及优化方面表现不佳<ref name="ignps3review2" /><ref name="europcreview2" />。另外，有评论家称赞游戏的世界观和其中精巧的机械<ref name="xplayps3review" /><ref name="ginformerps3review">{{cite web |url=http://gameinformer.com/NR/exeres/360AAE13-1A02-4AB5-B84E-A773CD6F7FA9.htm |title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition Review |last=Miller |first=Matt |work=PlayStation 3 |publisher=''[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]'' |accessdate=2009-05-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080611161438/http://gameinformer.com/NR/exeres/360AAE13-1A02-4AB5-B84E-A773CD6F7FA9.htm |archivedate=2008-06-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，称其玩法可与《{{link-en|希魔复活|Bionic Commando (arcade)}}》和《[[洛克人系列|洛克人]]》相比<ref name="1uppcreview" /><ref name="gspypcreview" />。与其他射击游戏的剧情设定（如[[二战|二战]]）相比，E.D.N. III的冰原设定更是大受欢迎<ref name="1up360review" /><ref name="ign360review2">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/01/06/lost-planet-extreme-condition-review-2?page=2|title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition Review (page 2)|last=Brudvig|first=Erik|date=01-05-2007|work=Xbox 360|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=2009-04-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019230151/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/01/06/lost-planet-extreme-condition-review-2?page=2|archivedate=2012-10-19}}</ref><ref name="gspypcreview2">{{cite web|url=http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/lost-planet-extreme-condition/801144p2.html|title=Lost Planet — Page 2|last=Kuo|first=Li C.|date=07-02-2007|publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|work=PC|accessdate=2009-04-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090726034223/http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/lost-planet-extreme-condition/801144p2.html|archivedate=2009-07-26}}</ref>。[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]评论：“（关卡设定）令人回味，普通的城市废墟、飞船内部、或燃烧的二战战场可做不到这一点”<ref name="gspy360review" />。让玩家为了生存而不断地寻找[[热能|热能]]的系统被认为很新颖，尽管这不是很有挑战性<ref name="gspypcreview2"/><ref name="europcreview">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/r_lostplanet_pc|title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition Review — Page 1 // PC|last=Walker|first=John|date=07-02-2007|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|accessdate=2009-04-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090503035849/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/r_lostplanet_pc|archivedate=2009-05-03}}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]的艾瑞克·布拉德維格（Erik Brudvig）说：“在大多数时候，热能消失的不够快是一个问题，但它确实很好的促动玩家去迎接下一个挑战”<ref name="ign360review">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/01/06/lost-planet-extreme-condition-review-2|title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition Review|last=Brudvig|first=Erik|date=01-05-2007|work=Xbox 360|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019230157/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/01/06/lost-planet-extreme-condition-review-2|archivedate=2012-10-19}}</ref>。

《失落的星球》Xbox 360和PC版本的画面得到了广泛好评<ref name="gspotpcreview" /><ref name="europcreview2" />。[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]评论：“在Xbox 360上，（游戏的）一些视觉效果令人印象深刻”<ref name="vg360review2" />。其他评论者提到其视觉效果为“惊人的”<ref name="europcreview2" />，“华丽的”<ref name="gpro360review">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/93628/lost-planet-extreme-condition/ |title=Review: Lost Planet: Extreme Condition |last=Three Ring Circus |date=01-12-2007 |work=Xbox 360 |publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]] |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203143328/http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/93628/lost-planet-extreme-condition/ |archivedate=2009-02-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，和“出色的”<ref name="palgn360review">{{cite web |url=http://palgn.com.au/xbox-360/6348/lost-planet-extreme-condition-review/ |title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition Review — Xbox 360 |last=Jastrzab |first=Jeremy |date=01-08-2007 |publisher=PALGN |accessdate=2009-05-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727193712/http://palgn.com.au/xbox-360/6348/lost-planet-extreme-condition-review/ |archivedate=2009-07-27 }}</ref>。然而，PlayStation 3版的画面却不那么好<ref name="xplayps3review">{{cite web |url=http://g4tv.com/xplay/reviews/1741/Lost_Planet_Extreme_Conditions.html |title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition — PS3 Review Videos |last=Marriott |first=Scott Alan |publisher=''[[X-Play|X-Play]]'' |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080327032646/http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/reviews/1741/Lost_Planet_Extreme_Conditions.html |archivedate=2008-03-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="gdailyps3review">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/games/lost-planet/playstation-3/game-reviews/review/6960/1965/ |title=Lost Planet on PlayStation 3 Review |last=Workman |first=Robert |date=2008-03-03 |publisher=GameDaily |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022185745/http://www.gamedaily.com/games/lost-planet/playstation-3/game-reviews/review/6960/1965/ |archivedate=2008-10-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。澳大利亚的{{link-en|PALGN|PALGN}}说：“Xbox 360版的整体效果和运行速度完胜PlayStation 3版，当你把两个版本放在一起比较时差别尤其明显。这令人非常失望，因为PlayStation 3版可是比Xbox 360版晚了一年发布”<ref name="palgnps3review">{{cite web|url=http://palgn.com.au/playstation-3/10645/lost-planet-extreme-condition-review/|title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition Review|last=Jastrzab|first=Jeremy|date=2008-03-19|work=PlayStation 3|publisher=PALGN|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727193646/http://palgn.com.au/playstation-3/10645/lost-planet-extreme-condition-review/|archivedate=2009-07-27}}</ref>。音效方面，收到的评价从一般到好均有<ref name="ignps3review2" /><ref name="gspot360review" /><ref name="gdailyps3review" />，唯其配音遭到了广泛的批评<ref name="europcreview2" /><ref name="vg360review2" /><ref name="xplayps3review" />。如GameSpot就表示：“配音很生硬，其中最糟糕的情况下听起来非常虚假”<ref name="gspot360review" />。

Akrid的设计受到表扬<ref name="gspotpcreview" />，评论称其可与《{{link-en|装甲龙骑兵|Panzer Dragoon (series)}}》、《[[沙丘系列小說|沙丘]]》和《[[星河戰隊_(電影)|星河戰隊]]》中的怪物相比<ref name="ign360review2" /><ref name="eurofirst">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/fi_lostplanet_x360_3|title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition First Impressions — Page 1 // Xbox 360|last=Bramwell|first=Tom|date=2006-11-13|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415235116/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/fi_lostplanet_x360_3|archivedate=2009-04-15}}</ref><ref name="vg360review">{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/xbox360/lost_planet_extreme_condition/review.html|title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition Review for Xbox 360|last=Orry|first=Tom|date=10-01-2007|publisher=VideoGamer.com|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010161920/http://www.videogamer.com/xbox360/lost_planet_extreme_condition/review.html|archivedate=2008-10-10}}</ref>。IGN评论：“巨型地龙看起来像是将[[弗兰克·赫伯特|弗兰克·赫伯特]]所想象的巨大飞蛾直接撕裂而生成，其中的线条既美丽又可怕，整个设计超凡脱俗”<ref name="ign360review2" />。与巨大Akrid的BOSS战被认为是大规模和史诗级的战斗<ref name="euro360review2" /><ref name="ginformerps3review" />；PALGN将它们与《[[汪达与巨像|汪达与巨像]]》相提并论<ref name="palgn360review" />。角色设计得到了消极评论，尤其是主角韦恩的设计。评论家批评他的名字<ref name="gspot360review" /><ref name="ginformerps3review" />缺乏个性<ref name="euro360review2" />并且落入俗套<ref name="ignps3review2" /><ref name="europcreview" />。另一个常见的抱怨是关于其剧情<ref name="ign360review3" />；评论家认为其令人困惑、费解，且翻译质量低下<ref name="gspot360review" /><ref name="palgn360review" /><ref name="palgnps3review" />。GameSpot表示：“最初游戏讲述了一个关于复仇的故事。但是，随着剧情的展开，越来越多令人费解的文字让整个剧情失控”<ref name="gspotpcreview" />。

《失落的星球》多人游戏部分得到了好坏不一的评价。评论家一般都很高兴游戏给了玩家多种选择<ref name="xplayps3review" /><ref name="ginformerps3review" />，但令人失望的是，玩家只能通过联网进行多人游戏，而不能在单台机器上多人合作<ref name="ign360review3" /><ref name="euro360review2" />。[[GamePro|GamePro]]批评了Xbox 360版本的配对系统，如果主机掉线，所有加入此游戏的玩家都将断开连接。PC版本在发行后遇到很多技术问题，使得很多玩家无法加入在线游戏<ref name="gspotpcreview" />。

=== 销售情况 ===
截至2007年9月，Xbox 360版游戏的演示版居Xbox Live下载排行榜第二<ref name="gsutrademo">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=15566|title=Microsoft: Xbox Live To Hit 10m Users In June 2008|last=Alexander|first=Leigh|date=2007-09-20|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728183000/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=15566|archivedate=2009-07-28}}</ref>，并且在2007年的最常玩在线游戏排行榜上位居第十<ref name="gsutralive">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=16051|title=Top 2007 Xbox Live Games Show Retro Success|last=Boyer|first=Brandon|date=01-07-2008|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090510021730/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=16051|archivedate=2009-05-10}}</ref>。Xbox 360版本在北美和英国都十分畅销<ref name="gsutra022307">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12850|title=Supreme Commander, Crackdown Storm Real-Time Charts|last=Cowan|first=Danny|date=2007-02-23|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727221841/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12850|archivedate=2009-07-27}}</ref><ref name="gsutra030207">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12916|title=Saling The World: Will Wright vs. Giant Robots|last=Cowan|first=Danny|date=03-02-2007|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727221846/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12916|archivedate=2009-07-27}}</ref><ref name="gsutra042707">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=13701|title=Pokémon Stomps U.S. Charts, FFXII Spinoff Rules Japan|last=Cowan|first=Danny|date=2007-04-27|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070831092617/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=13701|archivedate=2007-08-31}}</ref>，其中2007年1月以32万9000份成为美国最畅销的Xbox360游戏<ref name="gsutrajan07">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12841|title=U.S. January Game Sales Up 53%, Wii Outsells PS3|last=Gamasutra Staff|date=2007-02-21|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727221836/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12841|archivedate=2009-07-27}}</ref>。2007年1月17日，卡普空公司宣布游戏全球销量达到一百万<ref name="gsutramill">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12426|title=Newsbriefs: Games That Matter, Lost Planet Ships A Million, Battlestations XBL Demo|last=Gamasutra Staff|date=2007-01-17|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728182934/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12426|archivedate=2009-07-28}}</ref>。截至2007年3月底已售出137万份<ref name="gsutra1.37">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=14520|title=Capcom Rules Out Merger, Hints At Acquisitions|last=Jenkins|first=David|date=2007-06-29|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728182949/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=14520|archivedate=2009-07-28}}</ref>。发行一年后，日本Xbox360版已售出61,555份，成为该地区销量第十的Xbox 360游戏<ref name="gsutrajapan">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=16768|title=Blue Dragon Tops Lifetime Xbox 360 Software Sales In Japan|last=Boyer|first=Brandon|date=2007-12-27|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193618/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=16768|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref>。PlayStation 3版在日本和北美很畅销<ref name="gsutra022208">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17553|title=Saling The World: Professor Layton, Apollo Justice Impact DS Charts in U.S.|last=Cowan|first=Danny|date=2008-02-22|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090825104008/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17553|archivedate=2009-08-25}}</ref><ref name="gsutra022908">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17686|title=Saling The World: The Sims 2: FreeTime, Gundam Lead Worldwide Charts|last=Cowan|first=Danny|date=2008-02-29|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727221857/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17686|archivedate=2009-07-27}}</ref>，并在发布34周后成为英国销售排行榜的冠军<ref name="gsutraps3uk">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17712|title=Touch! Generations Dominate UK Sales Charts|last=Jenkins|first=David|date=03-04-2008|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728183013/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17712|archivedate=2009-07-28}}</ref>。2008年12月亚马逊将此游戏放到首页推荐之后，北美版销量大增<ref name="gsutra12122008">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=21496|title=Saling The World: Wii Music Tops Wii Sales; Gears of War 2 Leads on 360|last=Cowan|first=Danny|date=2008-12-12|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207091424/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=21496|archivedate=2009-02-07}}</ref>。这两个家用机版在美国游戏租赁公司{{link-en|GameFly|GameFly}}中都很流行<ref name="gsutragfly1">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12656|title=Crackdown, Xbox 360 Headline GameFly Charts|last=Dobson|first=Jason|date=02-05-2007|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728182944/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12656|archivedate=2009-07-28}}</ref><ref name="gsutragfly2">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17610|title=GameFly: Frontlines Leads Charge on Charts|last=Alexander|first=Leigh|date=2008-02-25|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727221852/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17610|archivedate=2009-07-27}}</ref><ref name="gsutragfly3">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17336|title=GameFly: Turok, Devil May Cry 4 Dominate|last=Alexander|first=Leigh|date=02-11-2008|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090820044638/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17336|archivedate=2009-08-20}}</ref>。2007年初，Xbox 360版本成为了该公司全游戏平台中出租量最高的游戏<ref name="gsutragfly4">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12576|title=Lost Planet, 360 Once Again Dominate GameFly Charts|last=Dobson|first=Jason|date=2007-01-29|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728182939/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12576|archivedate=2009-07-28}}</ref>。在日本，PC版的销量名列前五<ref name="gsutrapc">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=14682|title=Saling The World: Dragon Quest Swords Tops Sales in Debut Week|last=Cowan|first=Danny|date=2007-07-13|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728182954/http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=14682|archivedate=2009-07-28}}</ref>。这两个版本的《失落的星球》的总销量为280万份<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/business/salesdata.html |title=Total Sales Units |publisher=[[Capcom|Capcom]] |accessdate=2010-04-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140327174103/http://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/business/salesdata.html |archivedate=2014-03-27 }}</ref>。

=== 所获奖项 ===
本游戏的Xbox 360版本获得了[[IGN|IGN]]的“编辑选择奖”<ref name="ign360review3" />和[[莱比锡游戏展|莱比锡游戏展]]的“最佳Xbox 360游戏奖”<ref name="gspotleipzig">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/lost-planet-extreme-condition-awarded-best-xbox-360-game-at-leipzig-games-convention-6157224|title=Lost Planet: Extreme Condition Awarded Best Xbox 360 Game at Leipzig Games Convention|date=09-07-2006|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104103356/http://www.gamespot.com/news/lost-planet-extreme-condition-awarded-best-xbox-360-game-at-leipzig-games-convention-6157224|archivedate=2012-11-04}}</ref>。它还在2006年的[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]展会上得到了[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的“最佳动作游戏奖”<ref name="gsutra1up">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=9371|title=1UP Names Best of E3 2006 Award Winners|last=Dobson|first=Jason|date=2006-05-18|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081221223532/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=9371|archivedate=2008-12-21}}</ref>和一个2007年的日本游戏“卓越奖”<ref name="gsutrajaward">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=15560|title=Wii Sports, Monster Hunter Top Japan Game Awards|last=Alexander|first=Leigh|date=2007-09-20|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081221163402/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=15560|archivedate=2008-12-21}}</ref>。游戏的市场营销活动也获得了多个奖项，在2007年电子互动营销协会举办的M16奖中，限量版包装得到“金奖”，宣传海报和宣传视频得到“银奖”<ref name="gsutramarketing">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=13866|title=2007 MI6 Award Winners Announced|last=Gamasutra Staff|date=05-09-2007|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070913235321/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=13866|archivedate=2007-09-13}}</ref>。在2007年的游戏音频网络协会上，《失落的星球》获得了最佳电影/过场音频和年度音效设计奖的提名，但最终均不敌《[[战争机器|战争机器]]》<ref name="gangaward">{{cite web|url=http://www.audiogang.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=160&Itemid=189|title=5th Annual Game Awards|publisher=Game Audio Network Guild|accessdate=2009-05-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727202359/http://www.audiogang.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=160&Itemid=189|archivedate=2009-07-27}}</ref>。

== 续作 ==
《{{link-en|失落的星球2|Lost Planet 2}}》作为《失落的星球：极限状态》的续作于2009年2月23日公布，Xbox Live上发布的视频显示E.D.N. III上的冰雪已经融化并开始出现茂密的丛林。卡普空表示游戏将包括一些重大更新，包括改良版的MT Framework引擎和新的多人协作战役<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamezine.co.uk/news/formats/xbox360/capcom-top-secret-game-announcement-now-available-download-$1271782.htm |title=Capcom Top Secret Game Announcement now available for download |date=2009-02-23 |publisher=GameZine |accessdate=2009-02-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090224215907/http://www.gamezine.co.uk/news/formats/xbox360/capcom-top-secret-game-announcement-now-available-download-%241271782.htm |archivedate=2009-02-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="lp2 announce">{{cite web |url=http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/LOST-PLANET-2/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d802434307ed?DownloadType=GameVideo#LiveZone |title=Capcom Top Secret Game Announcement Xbox LIVE Marketplace Download Page |date=2009-02-23 |accessdate=2009-03-12 |publisher=[[Xbox|Xbox]] |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101030030224/http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/LOST-PLANET-2/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d802434307ed/?DownloadType=GameVideo#LiveZone |archivedate=2010-10-30 }}</ref>。《失落的星球2》后于2010年5月发布<ref name="GamerZines" />。《{{link-en|失落的星球3|Lost Planet 3}}》于2012年4月10日公布，游戏最终于2013年8月全球发售<ref name="LP3releaseCVG" />。

